Where is ad credit can test first ?

To test ad credits, you first need to ensure your account meets certain conditions. The account must complete and pass business verification, and accumulate over $5,000 in spend. Once these conditions are met, you can establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality to be enabled for you.
